<br>
I shouldnt have to restate that as you of all people should be smart enough to know that.  Jefnfry (Who is by far one of the kindest druids I have ever met) has his own guild.  Small now, but certain to grow, I do however suspect he will not be getting a Mask of the Dragonslayer anytime soon.  So your upgrade isnt feasible for a while.  And I've already said that the items may be upgraded even if it takes a while.<br>
<br>
You cant possibly award loot based on the fact that &quot;Soandso will get something better down the road so they dont deserve this&quot;.  I never said that you could, and I think everybody knows that you can not.<br>
<br>
